{"tid":2134464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[康城要人] 有間小店被藍絲前委會同管理處迫遷 要佢即日停業！","createTime":"2020-07-31T17:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T00:43:05.000Z","uid":83161,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a31b4a7542a09d1389edfce7f36ead43871304","tid":2134464,"uid":83161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）即日休業一事完全無諮詢過康城居民意見<br />\n2）個五十個所謂投訴既人無出過名<br />\n3）反而有過百名支持怡滿記既居民實名簽署<br />\n4）因地政總署52a(1)而違反 但管理處既經理完全答唔到係咩條款 <br />\n5）個位置亦係管理處提供 而家又話間檔違反條例<br />\n       <span class=\"red\">康城管理處收左八個月租金 知法犯法</span><br />\n6）聽日8月1號十點就要檔主執哂所有野走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔥【 ＃領都怡滿記爭議事宜】🔥<br />\n       &diams;️ ＃本人為應屆領都業委會主席李栢棠，昨晚收到客務務處電郵，知悉約有50個住戶反對怡滿記於六七座L5走廊側服務住戶，更先後向<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">食環署、民政署、消防署和地政署</span></span>等政府機構作不同的投訴，客務處亦鑑於屋苑近日有4宗確診個案，為釋公眾疑慮，＃故港鐵建議怡滿記暫停營業。<br />\n     🚩事件茲事體大，本人於此亦謹作回應數點：<br />\n（1）＃怡滿記由今屆業委會引入，目的是紓緩街坊「購物難」的問題；<br />\n（2）怡滿記與任何一位業委成員，皆沒有親屬或利益關係；<br />\n（3）＃怡滿記每個月支付約25000元場地費，一年便是30萬元，＃全數撥歸屋苑管理費帳戶，每一位小業主皆受惠；<br />\n（4）怡滿記於疫情期間，堅持繼續營業為街坊提供新鮮食品的購買服務，讓住戶無需外出「迫街市」和「迫超巿」，避免人群聚集而感染肺炎的風險。在此，＃我們謹向怡滿記同寅致以由衷感激！<br />\n（5）鑑於有人以不同手段企圖置怡滿記於死地，我們謹期望他們懂得聆聽一下不同的聲音，尊重一下不同的需求，大家求同存異，和諧共處，讓街坊鄰里皆能享受不同的服務。<br />\n      🚩最後，＃業委會仍與港鐵管理處協調及磋商怡滿記事宜，當有結果，定必盡快向大家公佈。<br />\n<br />\n領都業委會主席栢棠<br />\n2020年7月30日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">康城人 聽日十點 怡滿記檔口集合</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a95a4892a6340aca39750f82a889b07e1875a51","tid":2134464,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c240b9e1bfb3525d87c4882febca313a228cc6b5","tid":2134464,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f0915a5ce7a6786ca7bcdf2e66fff04ed0434e","tid":2134464,"uid":57469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:29:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab8736575373cff697da55675f50a7107d7e9dd","tid":2134464,"uid":83161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVRLaMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVRLaMa.jpg&h=c522512a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vxivMb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vxivMb.jpg&h=5320f17d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4447233e14e51d87c521943d1d547d6834db301b","tid":2134464,"uid":15072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:31:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b36eb5f27e1da6df07c3b9f98193aa9cf6283f5c","tid":2134464,"uid":83161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8pwQMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi